    <strong>What this shows:</strong> Whether customers felt the box was worth the price.
    Each bar stacks to 100% — new and recurring customers are combined using a weighted average.
    <br><br>
    <strong>Key insight:</strong> A rising "Poor" rate in hate boxes signals a value problem — items may be priced too high relative to perceived quality, or the box mix is not hitting the mark.
  </div>`);
}

